    "body": "Do you want to open a pull request that gives a warning?\n\nI think the real check is actually that the _read_ location is missing - so I guess the check should be:\n\n``` python\nif os.path.exists(src) and not os.path.exists(readme):\n```\n\nIPython really does not work if the profile directory cannot be made.\n"
