    "updated_at": "2013-03-27T11:16:54Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "What's the status on this? Is the os.path.exists(src) going to be added to master? \n\nThe problem with py2exe and pyinstaller packed python code is that the source \"README_STARTUP\" does not exists, because it was not packed. The profile directory often does. Since src at runtime can be a generated path name there is no way to additionally provide the file.\n\nAn alternative way is not to copy README_STARTUP but just to create it from the python code.\n"
  },
