    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Another issue with using ipython from a pyinstaller packed version is that from site import _Helper does not work. This seems to largely affect Windows builds. A work around is to remove the import and copy the _Helper class from site.py into core/interactiveshell.py.\n"
